{"tid":955964,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那企業級「Ant-design」Library 觸發聖誕彩蛋，俾人屌到仆街","createTime":"2018-12-26T01:03:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-26T21:22:23.000Z","uid":11598,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b2c44ff31892cb0877bc2f2fe071dc9a79166617","tid":955964,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T01:03:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ant.design\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fant.design&d=VEnvoTX589ayptzzh3AaWTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=79bdd9bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ant.design</a><br />\n呢個叫 Ant Design 嘅component 係由阿里巴巴嘅螞蟻金服嗰team人做嘅<br />\n話說係 9 月嗰陣有個contributor 就push 咗個聖誕彩蛋嘅 commit 係幫個component 嘅button 加啲積雪同埋有啲「HO HO HO」嘅字，同埋set好係聖誕節果日就會觸發<br />\n咁問題就嚟嘞 因為呢舊嘢好多地方都有用，包括咗啲國企/ 政府相關嘅網站<br />\n最重要係今年中國出咗批示唔俾過聖誕節 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即刻俾人屌到仆街<br />\n有啲developers 就話已經俾人炒咗 早啲過年咁話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢度有冇人中伏？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n殘體 Github issue<br />\n<a href=\"https://github.com/ant-design/ant-design/issues/13848\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fant-design%2Fant-design%2Fissues%2F13848&d=VEnvoTX589ayptzzh3AaWTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=b1ec24ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/ant-design/ant-design/issues/13848</a><br />\n<br />\n英文 Github issue<br />\n<a href=\"https://github.com/ant-design/ant-design/issues/13849\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fant-design%2Fant-design%2Fissues%2F13849&d=VEnvoTX589ayptzzh3AaWTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=3eb40ba9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/ant-design/ant-design/issues/13849</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/R7bE2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FR7bE2.png&h=9e668d79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢